    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Matter of fact, we took in a couple-- people from the other side of Poland, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they said they are-- they are killing people, and they're putting them in jail.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
