      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that they can raid our businesses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was no good though.",
      "word_count": 6
